extendedInfo.description: Mother Tongue Ink presents We'Moon Mobile: daily astrological & moon data through 2011 with articles, poems and featured art.- View moon phases- See astrological bodies' transits- Search for full/new moons, Mercury retrograde/direct, sun/moon eclipse times, and more!- Automatically adjusts for your device's timezone

reviews.title: Clean & Simple
reviews.comment: I only wish I could use it like a real calender program or upload the \'Important Days\' to my Android Calender!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Best yearlong info summaries!
reviews.comment: Tells what each sign\'s year will be about.  Even specific dates to pay attention to. Also, such amazing poetry & art, along w/great teachings about astrology.
reviews.author: Brook Lujan
